	   <tr><td colspan=2>It depends on the type of Boss mob you are after really.&nbsp;&nbsp;During a raid, Enchanters will do some or all of the following:<br><br>1. Maintain buffs e.g. (Clarity/Haste/GRM) etc<br>2. Tash mobs to lower resists for other spells<br>3. Slow mobs with if Shaman isn't present.<br>4. Mez/Charm unexpected additional mobs<br>5. Cast Mana Seive/Theft of Thought to prevent mobs from casting Complete Heal<br>6. Chain Cast Rune to help healers on Main Assist<br><br>Those cover about 95% of the things I generally do in a raid situation.<br><br>Best Regards,<br><br>Calanctus of Sol Ro<br>lvl 60 Phantasmist<br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
