	   <tr><td colspan=2>In response to your survey:<br><br>1.&nbsp;&nbsp;Im lvl 60<br>2.  I enjoy being in groups most.<br>3.  When I need to solo, I root/dot and med or use a  fear/pet/dot combo.  I &quot;heal&quot; pet using bedlam.<br>4.  When in group my preference is to pull 10-20 mobs and use AE stun/nuking tactics to kill them all.<br>5.  I prefer to be where the action is.  Whether it's indoor or outdoor doesn't matter to me.<br>6.  Grouping Loadout: fetter, pbae stun1, tash/pbae stun2, GoK/Dazzle, forlorn deeds/ae mez, debuff/nuke swap slot, buff swap slot, theft of thought.<br> Soloing Loadout:  fetter, pbae stun, fear, GoK/Dazzle, forlorn deeds, debuff/nuke swap slot, buff swap slot, theft of thought <br><br>7.  My enchanter is my main character.<br><br>8.  I like most the challenge and versatility of playing style that an enchanter has.<br><br>Best Regards,<br><br>Calanctus of Sol Ro<br>lvl 60 Phantasmist<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
